rows.label: tlk70000010_01_msg0001
rows.name:
My skin's all rough today. I must
have not had enough sleep.
What do you think?

rows.label: tlk70000010_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Of course, the body doesn't just take
care of itself. And it's tough to get the
stuff for that round here.

rows.label: tlk70000010_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Drivers can give themselves a boost
with accessories, Blades with Aux
Cores, right?

rows.label: tlk70000010_01_msg0004
rows.name:
They all have their own particular
effects. Like some are restorative, some
are offensive, some defensive.

rows.label: tlk70000010_01_msg0005
rows.name:
Iira's a bit behind the times, if you
ask me. Invidia's where it's at right now
in its technology.

rows.label: tlk70000010_01_msg0006
rows.name:
I hear there's this thing that works
directly on the cells to make them
lustrous and moist. I'd love to try it.
